    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1794012423" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9466360630240952028"><strong>Good book about a forgotten battle</strong><br/><br/>This is a fine book about an untested Irish unit that served under the auspices of an unprepared UN in the Congo crisis of the early 1960s. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


