<div id="review_3704341732" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3704341732" />
    <a title="Tom Watson" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/90498097-tom-watson"><img alt="Tom Watson" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3704341732?book_show_action=true">Dec 19, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Tom Watson" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Tom Watson" href="/user/show/90498097-tom-watson">Tom Watson</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/32147650-siege-at-jadotville">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3704341732" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6172475074341510115"><strong>Good summary of largely forgotten UN action in the Congo</strong><br/><br/>Good book, focused on A Co which fought heroically at Jadotville in the Congo shortly after independence was won from Belgium. Not a lot of tactical analysis as it focused on one company and the inept prosecution of military action by the UN forces. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

